{"tid":555425,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【終年64歲】樂隊MR. BIG鼓手Pat Torpey病逝","createTime":"2018-02-09T12:03:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-28T17:05:20.000Z","uid":34156,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"c58b500b98bfa37dd4ad9342a5de6aac57959cf6","tid":555425,"uid":34156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T12:03:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/09/200347_acb0d1932577479bd0103a52aca24fdb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F09%2F200347_acb0d1932577479bd0103a52aca24fdb.png&h=cd8db8cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【終年64歲】樂隊MR. BIG鼓手Pat Torpey病逝<br />\n<br />\n即時娛樂  2018-02-09 13:07:46 HKT\t <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n樂隊MR. BIG鼓手Pat Torpey病逝。<br />\n<br />\nPat Torpey因柏金遜症引發的病症過世。<br />\n<br />\nMR. BIG是90年代有名的美式硬搖滾樂隊，名曲《To Be with You》街知巷聞。<br />\n美國著名搖滾樂隊MR. BIG鼓手Pat Torpey，於當地時間周三病逝，終年64歲。其家人、隊友及經理人請求各界於這個艱難時刻給予私人空間。<br />\n<br />\n聲明中指Pat Torpey因柏金遜症引發的病症過世，樂隊結他手Richie Kotzen指：「很傷心，聽到我的好友及前隊友Pat Torpey過身。我們有很多時間在世界各地開巡唱、做音樂、與家人共度節日，甚至一起裝修房屋。Pat的幽默感與笑容令他一走進房間就很有氣氛。我很感激、感謝有你成為我重要的朋友、影響我的一生，你會被記住，充滿淚水，愛你。RIP我的朋友。」而樂隊主音Eric Martin就指Pat是他見過最強壯的人。<br />\n<br />\nMR. BIG是90年代有名的美式硬搖滾樂隊，名曲《To Be with You》街知巷聞。他們曾於2002年解散，但在2009年再重組，一直都有發佈新作並舉行巡唱，上年更發佈了新專輯《Defying Gravity》。"},{"pid":"a665a8108b30f228e3da67620b2f4e1cffd08848","tid":555425,"uid":62532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T12:33:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28ef5b085ed04bc1480c96d68df10814130a4d35","tid":555425,"uid":34156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T12:37:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj